features: 【AGHP technique】5×6mm heat pipes apply AGHP III technique, Solve the Inverse gravity effect caused by vertical / horizontal orientation,Up to 20000 hours of industrial service life, S-FDB bearings ensure long service life of air-cooler radiators. UL class a safety insulation low-grade, industrial White PBT + PC material to create high-quality products for you. The height is 148mm, Suitable for medium-sized computer case.

【PWM Fan】Model:TL-C12CW-S; Colorful and gorgeous ARGB light effects; Standard size PWM fan:120x120x25mm (4.72x4.72x0.98 inches); fan speed (RPM):1550rpm±10%; power port: 4pin; Voltage:12V; Air flow:66.17CFM(MAX); Noise Level≤25.6dB(A), the fan pairs efficient cool with low-noise-level, providing you an environment with both efficient cool and true quietness.
【Compatibility】The CPU cooler Socket supports: Intel:115X/1200/1700/17XX, AMD:AM4:AM5; For different CPU socket platforms, corresponding mounting plate or fastener parts are provided.

【Product specification】Thermalright AK120 SE WHITE ARGB; CPU Cooler dimensions: 120(L)x73(W)x148(H)mm (4.92x2.87x 5.83 inch); Product weight:0.64kg(1.4lb); heat sink material: aluminum, CPU cooler is equipped with metal fasteners of Intel & AMD platform to achieve better installation.

【Brand Overview】Thermalright is a Taiwan brand with more than 20 years of development. It has a certain popularity in the domestic and foreign markets and has a pivotal influence in the player market. We have been focusing on the research and development of computer accessories. R & D product lines include: CPU air-cooled radiator, case fan, thermal silicone pad, thermal silicone grease, CPU fan controller, anti falling off mounting bracket, support mounting bracket and other commodities.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: EXCELLENCE USER EXPERIENCE Premium THERMALRIGHT TF-4 thermal paste is also included with CPU cooler for the best out-of-the-box performance. Redesigned Thermalright SS2 mounting system offers easy installation process and optimal mounting pressure. 5 AGHP (ANTI-GRAVITY HEAT PIPE) TECHNOLOGY HEAT PIPES Common heat pipes heavily depend on gravity to achieve optimal performance. Heatsink equipped with THERMALRIGHT Special design AGHP Heat Pipes is not affected by the mounting direction. This ensures user’s cooler experience in different computer case designs. BALANCE PERFORMANCE TL-C12CW-S FAN Based on TL-C12 fan design, TL-C12CW-S fan series achieve optimal balance between performance and noise output, therefore they are all-around fan for heatsink or radiator use scenarios. The motor is equipped with S-FDB bearing for smooth operation and long life span. The S model comes with addressable RGB lighting for aesthetic performance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderfully Quiet AM5 Cooler.
reviews.reviewText: Built a tower this past weekend, and was concerned whether this was going to fit my AMD Ryzen 7 7700 cpu (AM5), and it fit it perfectly! You just use the AM4 instructions for the mounts, they are the same.This thing is super quiet, and even under CPU stress tests has kept it very cool.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Impressive all around
reviews.reviewText: This thing is dense. It weighs like more than a Pure Rock 2 and is quite a bit shorter and thinner. And has more heat pipes. Fin density is high. Cools like a champ. Included fan is very quiet and pushes enough air. Plus its argb. Bottom plate is extremely flat and smooth.Install is quick and easy for AM4.5600x staying around 73 after hours of Gaming.For the price there is nothing comparable. For twice the price there's nothing comparable.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My go-to for air cooling
reviews.reviewText: For low to medium wattage rigs, this is my go-to. You can always add another fan if needed on the back side. Great cooler for the price. I'll run them on Ryzen 5 and core i5 rigs any day.

La verdad le iba a poner la ventilacion de stock para el 12400f pero la verdad vi muy buenas valoraciones sobre este disipador, si no elegia este me iba a ir por un 212 evo pero decidi probarlo y la verdad es que no le pide nada al 212 evo mi hermano tiene uno junto con un 10400 entonces en eso me basé para probarlo y la verdad es que me sorprendio, jugando escuchando musica y aveces stremeando no pasa de los 70°Y por el precio pues creo que vale la pena recomendarlo, a mi me costo poco mas de 500mxn llevo aproximadamente poco mas de dos meses y no me ha decepcionado, aparte es argb y se sincroniza facil con el mystic light de msi10/10 banda si tienen poco dinero y quieren algo que les funcione bien lo recomiendo ampliamente y mas si lo encuentran en oferta.

reviews.reviewText: Su diseño es muy bueno, enfría muy bien, buena calidad y por el precio no hay nada mejor. Y el color en blanco es perfecto.
para reducir temperaturas y ruido sirve bien por su precio claro que no seran bajones de temperaturas como una liquida pero para evitarte problemas y sobre todo que sea silencioso cumple su funcion

reviews.reviewTitle: Ryzen 5 5600X Si lo enfria demaciado bien
reviews.reviewText: En mi opinión todo super bien con lo que batalle un poco fue con El ADD gen 2 tengo la rog strix b-550 F gaming y pues el ADD argb está al otro extremo de la placa pero todo de ahí es súper fácil de instalar le hice test con varios juegos diferentes y antes con el de stock mi procesador subía hasta 85c° a 93c° cuando instale el nuevo bajo a fluctuante un punto medio extraño fluctuaba la temperatura la primera vez que lo use en estado vegetal (inicio) estaba a 35c° grados y jugando juegos demandantes cómo Genshin,Halo,wz subía hasta 55c° grados al segundo día de su uso el estado vegetal subió a 56c° y cuando jugaba subía hasta los 77c° tercer día de uso casi volvió a su estado normal en si el disipador para jugar está entre 55 y 65c° es muy recomendable para redenderizado sube hasta 70c° pero lo mantiene estable con todo su máximo rendimiento muy recomendado
Muy buenos materiales y, trae los accesorios necesarios para instalar fácilmente
